CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `activity_logs` ( `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `activity` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `description` text, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `alter_tables` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `query` text NOT NULL, `status` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `fields` text, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `application_settings` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `setting_name` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT NULL, `setting_value` text CHARACTER SET utf8, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `autoresponders` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `autoresponder_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `order_no` int(11) DEFAULT '0', `perform_action_datetime_frequency` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `perform_action_datetime_count` int(11) DEFAULT '0', `email_subject` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT NULL, `is_active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `send_to_existing` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `meta_attributes` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `autoresponder_groups` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `is_start` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `smtp_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `meta_attributes` longtext, `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `bounces` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `process_bounce_report` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `host` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `port` mediumint(9) DEFAULT NULL, `username` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `password` varchar(1027) DEFAULT NULL, `folder` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `validate_certificates` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0', `bounce_encryption` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `delete_emails` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0', `processing_protocols` enum('pop','imap') DEFAULT NULL, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `pmta_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `test_status` varchar(50) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `is_active` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', PRIMARY KEY (`id`), KEY `pmta_id` (`pmta_id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=13 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `bounce_reasons` (`id` int(11) NOT NULL,`label` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,`code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `code_condition` enum('is','contains') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'is',  `reason` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,  `reason_condition` enum('is','contains') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'is',  `details` text,  `details_condition` enum('is','contains') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'is',  `type` enum('soft','hard','no_process') DEFAULT NULL,  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',  `is_default` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',  `sort_order` int(10) UNSIGNED DEFAULT NULL, `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,  `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `broadcast_links` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `broadcast_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `link` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `bug_replies` ( `id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `bug_id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL, `user_type` enum('client','staff') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'staff', `reply` text NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `bug_reports` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `section` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `priority` varchar(100) NOT NULL, `subject` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `description` text, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `status` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `campaigns` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 DEFAULT NULL, `subject` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL, `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `content_url` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `url` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `content_html` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8, `content_text` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `is_campaign_builder` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `campaign_schedules` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `type` enum('subscriber','segment','split_test') DEFAULT NULL, `list_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `segment_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `campaign_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `split_test_on` enum('lists','campaigns') DEFAULT NULL, `split_test_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `smtp_ids` text, `smtp_sequence` enum('batch','loop') DEFAULT 'batch', `sending_pattern` enum('sequential','random') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'sequential', `masked_domain` enum('not','smtp','custom') DEFAULT 'not', `masked_domain_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `send_campaign` varchar(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'now', `send_datetime` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `sender_option` enum('smtp','list','custom') DEFAULT 'smtp', `from_attributes` text, `notification_email` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `status` enum('processing','paused','complete','scheduled','scheduling','system paused','resumed') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'processing', `paused_reason` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL, `is_running` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `unsub_show` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `track_opens` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1', `track_clicks` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1', `hourly_speed` int(11) DEFAULT '-1', `threads` int(11) NOT NULL, `thread_no` int(11) DEFAULT '0', `thread_settings` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `emails_sent` int(11) DEFAULT '0', `campaign_type` varchar(16) DEFAULT NULL, `evergreen_data` text, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `is_save_criteria` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `start_datetime` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `end_datetime` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `current_smtp` int(11) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`), KEY `campaign_schedule_status_index` (`status`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `email_templates` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `content_html` longtext, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `is_default` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `events_queue_process` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `event_type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `event_action` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL, `action_type` varchar(15) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'instant or later', `data` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL, `record_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '1=> pending, 2=>processing, 3=>completed', `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `fbls` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `host` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `port` mediumint(9) DEFAULT NULL, `username` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `password` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `folder` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `validate_certificates` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0', `fbl_encryption` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `delete_emails` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0', `processing_protocols` enum('pop','imap') DEFAULT NULL, `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `groups` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `section_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `is_deleted` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `is_movable` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `parent_group_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=12 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

INSERT INTO `groups` (`id`, `name`, `section_id`, `is_deleted`, `is_movable`, `parent_group_id`, `user_id`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES(1, '..', 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),(2, 'Unsorted', 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, NULL, NULL);
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `links` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `link` text, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `lists` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `owner_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `owner_email` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `reply_email` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `bounce_email_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `is_deleted` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `validate` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `total_subscribers` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `export_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `download_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `import_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `list_custom_field` ( `list_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `custom_field_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, KEY `fk_list_id` (`list_id`), KEY `fk_custom_field_id` (`custom_field_id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `migrations` ( `migration` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `batch` int(11) NOT NULL) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `mumara_migrations` ( `migration` varchar(255) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`migration`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `notifications` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `title` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `description` text, `is_publish` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `packages` ( `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `package_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `role_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL, `lists_limit` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '-1', `subscribers_limit` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '-1', `smtps_limit` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '-1', `monthly_email_limit` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '-1', `daily_email_limit` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '-1', `hourly_email_limit` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '-1', `modules` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `list_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `segment_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `email_template_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL, `sending_domain_limit` int(11) NOT NULL, `allow_smtp` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `allow_tracking` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1', `additional_headers` text, `oversending` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `oversending_price` int(10) UNSIGNED DEFAULT NULL, `oversending_limit` int(10) UNSIGNED DEFAULT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`id`)) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `password_resets` ( `email` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `token` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `created_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL, KEY `password_resets_email_index` (`email`), KEY `password_resets_token_index` (`token`)) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE FUNCTION get_interval(frequency VARCHAR(50), count_val INT, created_at TIMESTAMP) RETURNS VARCHAR(50) BEGIN DECLARE interval_val VARCHAR(50); DECLARE interval_date TIMESTAMP; IF frequency IS NULL THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val MINUTE); ELSEIF frequency = 'minutes' THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val MINUTE); ELSEIF frequency = 'hours' THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val HOUR); ELSEIF frequency = 'days' THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val DAY); ELSEIF frequency = 'weeks' THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val WEEK); ELSEIF frequency = 'months' THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val MONTH); ELSEIF frequency = 'years' THEN SET interval_date = DATE_ADD(created_at, INTERVAL count_val YEAR); END IF; RETURN interval_date; END;
